ShLChV-KUr MShL-'aUrTSh MSL'y MDBUrH 'aL-HUr BTh-TShYVN.
VHYH K'yVPh-NVDD QN MShLCh ThHYYNH BNVTh MV'aB M'yBUrTh L'aUrNVN.
HBY'aV 'yTShH 'yShV PhLYLH ShYThY KLYL TShLK BThVK TShHUrYM SThUrY NDChYM NDD 'aL-ThGLY.
YGVUrV BK NDChY MV'aB HVY-SThUr LMV MPhNY ShVDD KY-'aPhS HMTSh KLH ShD ThMV UrMS MN-H'aUrTSh.
VHVKN BChSD KS'a VYShB 'yLYV B'aMTh B'aHL DVD ShPhT VDUrSh MShPhT VMHUr TShDQ.
ShM'yNV G'aVN-MV'aB G'a M'aD G'aVThV VG'aVNV V'yBUrThV L'a-KN BDYV.
LKN YYLYL MV'aB LMV'aB KLH YYLYL L'aShYShY QYUr-ChUrShTh ThHGV 'aK-NK'aYM.
KY ShDMVTh ChShBVN 'aMLL GPhN ShBMH B'yLY GVYM HLMV ShUrVQYH 'yD-Y'yZUr NG'yV Th'yV MDBUr ShLChVThYH NTShV 'yBUrV YM.
'yL-KN 'aBKH BBKY Y'yZUr GPhN ShBMH 'aUrYVK DM'yThY ChShBVN V'aL'yLH KY 'yL- QYTShK V'yL-QTShYUrK HYDD NPhL.
VN'aSPh ShMChH VGYL MN-HKUrML VBKUrMYM L'a-YUrNN L'a YUr'y'y YYN BYQBYM L'a-YDUrK HDUrK HYDD HShBThY.
'yL-KN M'yY LMV'aB KKNVUr YHMV VQUrBY LQYUr ChUrSh.
VHYH KY-NUr'aH KY-NL'aH MV'aB 'yL-HBMH VB'a 'aL-MQDShV LHThPhLL VL'a YVKL.
ZH HDBUr 'aShUr DBUr YHVH 'aL-MV'aB M'aZ.
V'yThH DBUr YHVH L'aMUr BShLSh ShNYM KShNY ShKYUr VNQLH KBVD MV'aB BKL HHMVN HUrB VSh'aUr M'yT MZ'yUr LV'a KBYUr.
